            <h2>Overview</h2>
            <p>This program will provide you with skills in computer game / simulation design and programming. You will create interactive 2D and 3D computer games for entertainment and serious real life scenario visualisation (virtual worlds). You will also learn how to research the market, develop business concepts and manage computer game/simulation development projects. This course is taught in partnership with the Academy of Interactive Entertainment (AIE).
</p>
